::Prowl/Killer::

Prowl kicks Killer in the head, the newcomer falling unconscious and flying 
down to the ground. Prowl swoops in to above Lunarpine, noticing that Shadow 
Wing had arrived to help him.

"I'm right above you," he says into his comm-link, "Need any more help?"
